          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Substance Abuse Prevention Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2022 various health and law enforcement programs related to the prevention and treatment of substance abuse and the reduction of demand for illicit drugs.</p> <p>The bill reauthorizes, among others, the following:</p> <ul> <li>the Office of National Drug Control Policy,</li> <li>the Drug-Free Communities Program,</li> <li>the High Intensity Drug Trafficking Areas Program, and</li> <li>the Drug Courts Program.</li> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
